<div class="new-user-page">
  <h1><%= t('registration.sign-up-heading') %></h1>
  <p>Make a free account on ALTopedia to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>post your own activities and help other teachers!</li>
    <li>write comments</li>
    <li>keep a list of your favorite activities!</li>
    <li>become a supporter and help keep the site running!</li>
  </ul>
  <p>E-mail addresses are used for account verification, password resets, and account-related information. There's no mailing list or other unsolicited e-mails. You can delete your account at any time.</p>
  <p>The site will send you an e-mail with a link to verify the account before you can use it. Please make sure that your e-mail address is entered correctly!</p>
  <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name), html: { class: "user-registration-form" } ) do |f| %>
    <%= render "devise/shared/error_messages" %>

    <%= recaptcha_tags %>
    <%= f.label :username, "Username", class: "form-label" %>
    <%= f.text_field :username, class: "form-textfield", minlength: 4, maxlength: 28 %>

    <%= f.label :email, "E-mail address", class: "form-label" %>
    <%= f.email_field :email, class: "form-textfield" %>

    <%= f.label :password, "Password (8 characters minimum)", class: "form-label" %>
    <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off", class: "form-textfield" %>

    <%= f.label :password_confirmation, "Confirm password", class: "form-label" %>
    <%= f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "off", class: "form-textfield" %>
    
    <div class="g-recaptcha" data-sitekey="6Lci9oMUAAAAACJEoSVu_sqgDxQA57AVGNPVqk0m"></div>
    <%= f.submit t('registration.sign-up-button'), class: "submit-button" %>
  <% end %>
  <p>Please fill out both of the Captchas on this page. Sorry about them, but they help stop spam bot accounts from signing up.</p>
  <%= link_to t('login.forgot_password'), new_user_password_path %>
  <%= link_to t('login.no-confirmation-instructions'), new_user_confirmation_path %>
</div>
